reviews.review_text: beautiful! thanks for taping this ted! the setlist and quality are perfect. anyone who gets this must get the shows from the two days preceding this show, being 3-24 and 3-25, which can also be found on the archive.
Look, for a while... While not the longest China>Rider ever, every note Jerry played was *crackling* with energy.  The power in that room that night was incredible. One of my favorites...
